casebody.data:
Monday, October 30, 2000

MOTION DOCKET

00-1794. Independence v. Power.

Cuyahoga App. No. 76534. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of execution of court of appeals’ judgment pending appeal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay of execution of court of appeals’ judgment pending appeal be, and hereby is, denied.

Resnick, J., not participating.
